re":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T07:01:33.000Z","msg":"Poly portfolio 點準備好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T20:22:26.000Z","msg":"唔好聽佢up乜都放落去，唔會俾你入。<br />\n<br />\n唔關個stream事唔好放，最好嘅project擺頭，organize好每個project process，由idea到execution，一定要有條理，凌亂難睇就唔會睇，零碎嘅垃圾寧願唔好放，你有另外sketxh想俾佢啲你drawing skill就interview先另外一份咁帶去，有啲stream可能有限放幾多個project，但你唔一定要塞滿，quality重要啲，如果你有一份特別差但放咗落去，佢對你印象會差咗。<br />\n<br />\n如果佢叫你交digital你就唔好打直排版，因為電腦moon係打橫睇。佢叫你叫實物你就做/印靚佢。而就算佢係叫你交digital，你interview都要印返一份實物去，你可以選擇重新當佢係本書咁排多一份再印，而因為interview嗰陣佢唔會咁認真睇你啲process，所以帶去嗰份應該係大圖為主，預佢每頁只會停留一兩秒，你要做到呢兩面內就俾人知你呢頁做緊咩。<br />\n<br />\n有問題再補充。<br />\n<br />\nsd grad"},{"pid":"5f5eda4ba4d7c1273e6ee6483084d50f320f224d","tid":1908124,"uid":145758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T04:07:26.000Z","msg":"想問under sociology既media and culture studies 同creative media 有咩分別"},{"pid":"9ae622379b3e961e524c139d6981dfa6d2ac8296","tid":1908124,"uid":305257,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"adaf32101ef67bc090c3d59de89d6900d2eecccc","tid":1908124,"uid":33875,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T05:12:31.000Z","msg":"點解CITY CM既同學十個有八個都咁囂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T06:56:58.000Z","msg":"囂又唔係好覺，但佢哋大部分都proud of自己係cm人係真嘅"},{"pid":"6968ecfd3a3e26aeba9ef029d6e768364a8738d4","tid":1908124,"uid":214885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f5eda4ba4d7c1273e6ee6483084d50f320f224d","tid":1908124,"uid":145758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T04:07:26.000Z","msg":"想問under sociology既media and culture studies 同creative media 有咩分別"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T11:50:22.000Z","msg":"Culture studies偏學術，Creative Media偏Art同埋Practical啲"},{"pid":"50d435503d4323dff2459c43fa10d95dccadefe1","tid":1908124,"uid":186668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T20:58:25.000Z","msg":"之前聽過有人講過cm 有分ba bsc <br />\nbsc 會重programming 多d?"},{"pid":"b0098613abe3a8369e5a0ece57ab842257035c88","tid"